无法用javac compile，找不到package。
javac WordMapper.java -cp $(/usr/bin/hadoop classpath)


29页的 hadoop com.sun.tools.javac.Main WordCount.java需要改成
	hadoop com.sun.tools.javac.Main WordCount.java WordMapper.java SumReducer.java

jar cf wc.jar WordCount.class WordMapper.class SumReducer.class

hadoop中ctrl+C不能真正终止作业，要使用hadoop job -list查看正在运行的作业，在使用kill命令hadoop -kill $JOB_IDclass Solution:
    def decodeString(self, s):
        stack = []
        stack.append(["", 1])
        num = ""
        for ch in s:
            if ch.isdigit():
                num += ch
            elif ch == '[':
                stack.append(["", int(num)])
                num = ""
            elif ch == ']':
                st, k = stack.pop()
                stack[-1][0] += st*k
            else:
                stack[-1][0] += ch
            #print(stack)
        return stack[0][0]